    <title>打破次元壁的桥梁 - Geyser介绍</title>
    <link href="http://sinangentoo.github.io/2021/03/28/Geyser%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/"/>
    <id>http://sinangentoo.github.io/2021/03/28/Geyser%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/</id>
    <published>2021-03-28T13:39:05.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-03-28T13:49:48.616Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>　　众所周知，从Minecraft PE诞生以来就与Java版势不两立，服务器更是如此，似乎永远是两条平行线。但是随着Geyser的发布与不断改善，似乎使得两个版本之间的隔阂或将被打破…</p><h2 id="什么是Geyser？"><a href="#什么是Geyser？" class="headerlink" title="什么是Geyser？"></a>什么是Geyser？</h2><p>　　简单来说，Geyser是一个连接Java服务器和基岩版服务器的转译器，能将Java服务器的packet转换成基岩版能够读懂的packet类型，从而实现基岩版能够进入Java服务器；由于Java版拥有一些基岩版没有的特性，同时Geyser还是在开发阶段，所以并没有那么完美，不过至少为我们提供了一个新的可能。<br><img src="https://i.niupic.com/images/2020/02/29/6Xak.jpeg"></p><h2 id="怎么使用？"><a href="#怎么使用？" class="headerlink" title="怎么使用？"></a>怎么使用？</h2><p>　　如果你是安卓，首先你得下载一个Termux，如果不知道什么是Termux或者怎么安装可以看我之前写的一篇<a href="http://pixel.fangkuai.art:8073/blog/index.php/archives/6/">博文</a>，本篇使用Termux演示。</p><h3 id="Termux前期准备（Linux和Windows可以跳过）"><a href="#Termux前期准备（Linux和Windows可以跳过）" class="headerlink" title="Termux前期准备（Linux和Windows可以跳过）"></a>Termux前期准备（Linux和Windows可以跳过）</h3><p>首先打开Termux，输入以下指令安装基础工具（建议以下步骤挂梯子，可能比较慢）：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;deb [trusted=yes] https://yadominjinta.github.io/files/ termux extras&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; <span class="variable">$PREFIX</span>/etc/apt/sources.list</span><br><span class="line">pkg <span class="keyword">in</span> atilo-cn</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>等待安装完成，然后输入以下指令正式开始安装Ubuntu：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">atilo pull ubuntu</span><br><span class="line">atilo run ubuntu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样就进入Ubuntu了，是不是很简单？<br>（不要问我为什么要装这个 Termux不能直接安装java）</p><h3 id="Java安装"><a href="#Java安装" class="headerlink" title="Java安装"></a>Java安装</h3><p>（安装发现速度慢也可以使用梯子，当然也可以自助还原）<br>接下来是安装java，也很简单，输入以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt update</span><br><span class="line">apt install openjdk-8-jdk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后可以去泡杯茶慢慢等了，安装完输入<code>java -version</code>查看是否有显示java版本号，如果显示说明安装成功。</p><h3 id="Geyser安装"><a href="#Geyser安装" class="headerlink" title="Geyser安装"></a>Geyser安装</h3><p>接下来就是最关键的一步了，请输入以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt install wget</span><br><span class="line">wget https://ci.nukkitx.com/job/Geyser/job/master/218/artifact/target/Geyser.jar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后恭喜你！安装完毕了！不过还需要一丢丢配置，我们先运行<code>java -jar Geyser.jar</code>，等待显示Done后运行<code>stop</code>暂停。好，输入ls，我们可以看到目录下多了个config.yml 让我们先分析一下结构，之后自己动手用vim改吧（vim怎么使用请自行搜索）</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># --------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># Geyser Configuration File</span><br><span class="line">#</span><br><span class="line"># A bridge between Minecraft: Bedrock Edition and Minecraft: Java Edition.</span><br><span class="line">#</span><br><span class="line"># GitHub: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;GeyserMC&#x2F;Geyser</span><br><span class="line"># Discord: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;discord.geysermc.org&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">#以上可以不用管，有兴趣自己翻译</span><br><span class="line"># --------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">bedrock:</span><br><span class="line">  # 这里是基岩服转发的设置，0.0.0.0相当于127.0.0.1</span><br><span class="line">  address: 0.0.0.0</span><br><span class="line">  # 同样，这是端口</span><br><span class="line">  port: 19132</span><br><span class="line">  # 服务器的闪动文字，自己改了就知道了</span><br><span class="line">  motd1: &quot;GeyserMC&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  motd2: &quot;Another GeyserMC forced host.&quot;</span><br><span class="line">remote:</span><br><span class="line">  # 这是要转发的服务器的地址，可以填域名也可以填ip</span><br><span class="line">  address: 127.0.0.1</span><br><span class="line">  # 这里是端口</span><br><span class="line">  port: 65535</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  # 这里如果是正版服就填online，不是就填offline</span><br><span class="line">  auth-type: online</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#以下基本不用改，自己翻译吧</span><br><span class="line">## the Xbox&#x2F;MCPE username is the key for the Java server auth-info</span><br><span class="line">## this allows automatic configuration&#x2F;login to the remote Java server</span><br><span class="line">## if you are brave&#x2F;stupid enough to put your Mojang account info into</span><br><span class="line">## a config file</span><br><span class="line">#userAuths:</span><br><span class="line">#  bluerkelp2: # MCPE&#x2F;Xbox username</span><br><span class="line">#    email: not_really_my_email_address_mr_minecrafter53267@gmail.com # Mojang account email address</span><br><span class="line">#    password: &quot;this isn&#39;t really my password&quot;</span><br><span class="line">#</span><br><span class="line">#  herpderp40300499303040503030300500293858393589:</span><br><span class="line">#    email: herpderp@derpherp.com</span><br><span class="line">#    password: dooooo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Relay the MOTD, player count and max players from the remote server</span><br><span class="line">ping-passthrough: false</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Maximum amount of players that can connect</span><br><span class="line">max-players: 100</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># If debug messages should be sent through console</span><br><span class="line">debug-mode: false</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Thread pool size</span><br><span class="line">general-thread-pool: 32</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Allow third party capes to be visible. Currently allowing:</span><br><span class="line"># OptiFine capes, LabyMod capes, 5Zig capes and MinecraftCapes</span><br><span class="line">allow-third-party-capes: true</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># bStats is a stat tracker that is entirely anonymous and tracks only basic information</span><br><span class="line"># about Geyser, such as how many people are online, how many servers are using Geyser,</span><br><span class="line"># what OS is being used, etc. You can learn more about bStats here: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;bstats.org&#x2F;.</span><br><span class="line"># https:&#x2F;&#x2F;bstats.org&#x2F;plugin&#x2F;server-implementation&#x2F;GeyserMC</span><br><span class="line">metrics:</span><br><span class="line">  # If metrics should be enabled</span><br><span class="line">  enabled: true</span><br><span class="line">  # UUID of server, don&#39;t change!</span><br><span class="line">  uuid: 7a990c6a-0cdc-4b37-8e04-ab8db60cd3c4</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>改完之后，再输入<code>java -jar Geyser.jar</code>启动Geyser，恭喜你，可以玩了！把Termux挂在后台锁着，然后打开Minecraft基岩版，IP输入127.0.0.1，端口输入你自己定的本地端口（一般都是19132），保存进去就可以玩了！最后放几张进Java服的截图：<br><img src="https://i.niupic.com/images/2020/02/29/6Xb2.jpg"><br><img src="https://i.niupic.com/images/2020/02/29/6Xb3.jpg"><br><img src="https://i.niupic.com/images/2020/02/29/6Xb4.jpg"><br><img src="https://i.niupic.com/images/2020/02/29/6Xb5.jpg"><br><img src="https://i.niupic.com/images/2020/02/29/6Xb7.jpg"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
